data.description: FULL RECENTLY RENOVATED ALL BRICK GEORGIAN (PLUS ADDITION) IN HIGHLY DESIRABLE POCKET OF ELMWOOD PARK ON TREE LINED STREET. WALKING DISTANCE TO OAK PARK COUNTRY CLUB AND PUBLIC TRANS. AMAZING CHARM OF A TRUE GEORGIAN WITH FREE FLOWING LAYOUT. WINDOWS, ROOF, ELECTRIC, PLUMBING AND EVERYTHING COSMETIC WAS REPLACED IN LATE 2020. 3 BEDROOM + FAMILY ROOM/REC ROOM + 2 BATH WITH ALL BRICK GARAGE. THE KITCHEN BOASTS STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, CALACATTA QUARTZ COUNTERTOPS AND WHITE SHAKER CABINETS. GREAT SIZED SIDE PLUS BACK YARD WITH PRIVACY FENCING ON ALL SIDES. MAIN LEVEL HAS AN OPEN LAYOUT  BETWEEN KITCHEN, LIVING ROOM AND DINING ROOM WITH ENGINEERED HARDWOOD FLOORS, GREAT SIZED BEDROOM AND FULL BATH. SECOND LEVEL FEATURES A HUGE PRIMARY BEDROOM, FULL BATH AND GREAT SIZED SECONDARY BEDROOM. LOWER LEVEL REC ROOM HAS SEPARATE ENTRANCE/EXIT TO THE BACK YARD. TRULY A MUST SEE! ***TAXES DO NOT REFLECT HOME OWNER EXEMPTION***
